{"tid":1593662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 用ANTI-CHINAZI  赤納粹符號打交叉 係無問題","createTime":"2019-09-25T07:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T15:40:09.000Z","uid":101392,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f9abcba61aa33ac385c26fea79f030370613ff42","tid":1593662,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:21:40.000Z","msg":"成個熱門喺度吹風話唔可以用CHINAZI，其實只要加返ANTI就可以照用<br />\n連ANTI CHINAZI都唔敢提<br />\n根本等如掩耳盜鈴 幫外國人斬腳趾避沙蟲<br />\n蒙住自己隻眼就當問題唔存在？<br />\n同當年張伯倫綏靖政策姑息納粹有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n德國人根本唔係玻璃心<br />\n佢地年年都紀念納粹大屠殺<br />\n周圍都有猶太人紀念碑 紀念館 <br />\n歷史教訓就係要成日提起先可以銘記<br />\n<br />\n其實nazi 喺外國無想像中咁禁忌<br />\n反而係少少野都鬧人nazi<br />\n譬如 grammar nazi<br />\n<br />\n西方網絡世界有個Godwin's Law，即係「當線上討論不斷變長時，參與者把用戶或其言行與納粹主義或希特拉類比的機率會趨於一（100%）」<br />\n根本nazi喺外國係好常用嘅類比<br />\n甚至去到濫用程度<br />\n我地只要解釋俾外國人知我地無濫用<br />\n中共的確有趨勢成為新一個納粹黨就得<br />\n紐約大學法學院教授Prof. Sharon Hom都係咁講"},{"pid":"eccc8b69227dbdceda529c6156c90c9ae6becf8f","tid":1593662,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:23:05.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"dba47d30b6e77e9c17f7a7f0cf984cf039550098","tid":1593662,"uid":115644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3fbWhs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3fbWhs.jpg&h=fa4fb7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kTQso8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kTQso8.jpg&h=403f413b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rAQ3No8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrAQ3No8.jpg&h=7d7381ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bef1d9be53dbd8dff01c7a58aae4eeb1fe0c604","tid":1593662,"uid":101392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:29:19.000Z","msg":"Sharon Hom: US must hold true to its core values-human rights, democracy &amp; freedom. HK shouldn&rsquo;t be made a bargaining chip. This is China vs the world, not 2 models of equal legitimacy. China&rsquo;s trying to replace the world order that emerged to prevent another Nazi Germany."},{"pid":"bd5479ace447721cb76605195dd4089a06e8fc24","tid":1593662,"uid":101392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/納粹中國-chinazi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%B4%8D%E7%B2%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-chinazi%2F&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9EyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=c10d383c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%B4%8D%E7%B2%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-chinazi%2F&h=72a37685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/納粹中國-chinazi/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年中國流亡作家余杰曾出版《納粹中國》一書，該書意旨簡而言之，就是敘述當今中國正出現邁向納粹德國的勢態。但我們活在 2019 年的香港，納粹中國可不是 future tense。而在過去一個月，Twitter 和 Instagram 都興起 Chinazi 這個 hashtag ，音近廣東話「癡乸綫」，語境也非常貼切。<br />\n<br />\n納粹德國所屠殺的人口，最高的估算達 2,600 萬人，可惜這個數字，一個大躍進就可以 KO。但撇開殺人的累積金多寶，論管治手段，21 世紀的中共竟也可以重現納粹雄風。納粹主義的全名是「國家民族社會主義」，而現在中國的政治意識形態，國家主權至上，要造民族復興的中國夢，加上憲法列明實行「中國特色社會主義」，在「習近平思想」帶引執行「極左」的施政風格，中國是完全符合納粹定義的極右法西斯政權。時代是會進步的，中共部份行徑比起納粹更為進化，例如將一個諾貝爾和平獎得主監禁至死，又譬如在新疆套用人臉識別 AI 建立自二戰以來最大規模的集中營。"},{"pid":"7f5e80c3683c0490ef8c4f3c60c13f2f5b6ffa69","tid":1593662,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"#AntiChinazi"},{"pid":"c59f6c7b0df74d33de1366874b5ec531482f4c14","tid":1593662,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:32:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-49279229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-49279229&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9EyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=dd5bd5f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-49279229</a><br />\n<br />\n黑斯蒂現任<span style=\"color: red;\">澳大利亞議會安全和情報聯合委員會主席</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他周四（8月9日）在《悉尼晨鋒報》上發表題為「機會和威脅--我們必須擦亮雙眼看中國」的長篇評論文章，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其中把中國崛起和納粹德國相提並論的段落引發關注</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n黑斯蒂寫道，中國試圖取代美國、主宰太平洋地區，這將威脅澳大利亞的主權和民主。<br />\n<br />\n他說，正如二戰期間（面臨入侵）的法國一樣，澳大利亞沒有做好凖備：和法國人一樣，澳大利亞沒有充分認識到「專權鄰國」的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n文章還說，西方一度相信，經濟自由可以自然而言地令中國走向民主。這是「我們的馬其諾防線」，會保障我們安全。就像法國人1940年代曾經相信，他們的鋼筋水泥城堡能夠抵禦納粹德國，最終導致「災難性的失敗」。"},{"pid":"67688b92b7df5c103710d93a3231359e7290cac0","tid":1593662,"uid":212731,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"最直接<br />\n直接話反法西斯 anti-fascist <br />\n唔使anti-chifascist/anti-chinazi咁麻煩<br />\n直接將中共/中國變成法西斯既代名<br />\nfascist=China=CCP=fascist<br />\n令人一見到中國就代號入座咁聯想到法西斯<br />\n簡單直接"},{"pid":"6d4ae1b640f67e1df173d7de72ec5f95234f45b4","tid":1593662,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdde7c8c5f68c5cbf4fbc4faac030cf3534f6560","tid":1593662,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c59f6c7b0df74d33de1366874b5ec531482f4c14","tid":1593662,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:32:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-49279229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-49279229&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9EyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=dd5bd5f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-49279229</a><br />\n<br />\n黑斯蒂現任<span style=\"color: red;\">澳大利亞議會安全和情報聯合委員會主席</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他周四（8月9日）在《悉尼晨鋒報》上發表題為「機會和威脅--我們必須擦亮雙眼看中國」的長篇評論文章，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其中把中國崛起和納粹德國相提並論的段落引發關注</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n黑斯蒂寫道，中國試圖取代美國、主宰太平洋地區，這將威脅澳大利亞的主權和民主。<br />\n<br />\n他說，正如二戰期間（面臨入侵）的法國一樣，澳大利亞沒有做好凖備：和法國人一樣，澳大利亞沒有充分認識到「專權鄰國」的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n文章還說，西方一度相信，經濟自由可以自然而言地令中國走向民主。這是「我們的馬其諾防線」，會保障我們安全。就像法國人1940年代曾經相信，他們的鋼筋水泥城堡能夠抵禦納粹德國，最終導致「災難性的失敗」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:32:47.000Z","msg":"根本連鬼佬自己都將中共類比為納粹"},{"pid":"9dfb2f7df6c9d388dd9f743e909eb714c268132d","tid":1593662,"uid":90987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:32:50.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n反係要加 X"},{"pid":"151b3cf96f9a5dcac7aab4ea0464421e85cc254e","tid":1593662,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各有各講<br />\n但最唔加味精係 anti China. </span>"},{"pid":"a0193c17131837387b1318bc94ec8260d8053841","tid":1593662,"uid":246242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:33:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5f59b45a913d2e4390a2b1561012d6348ef35c25","tid":1593662,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:35:16.000Z","msg":"納粹德國和中國再次被認真地相提並論是在2013年12月。當時，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">美國財經通訊社彭博社的新聞總編馬特.溫克勒（Matt Winkler）將習近平統治下的當今中國比作納粹德國</span></span>，將國際媒體在當今中國的運作比作當年在德國的運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.aboluowang.com/2017/1130/1033009.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2F2017%2F1130%2F1033009.html&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9EyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=a96b6799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.aboluowang.com/2017/1130/1033009.html</a>"},{"pid":"a6895bdf8b3f9fc89e8f39818e081fa08b2e0d14","tid":1593662,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:35:25.000Z","msg":"fascist Chi-na"},{"pid":"a61d3f5583901a4a3c5ab27999d74fadf19bef40","tid":1593662,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f59b45a913d2e4390a2b1561012d6348ef35c25","tid":1593662,"uid":101392,